{
  "texts": [
    "Nevertheless, we want to propose that: Cyber-social literacy learning is the complementary relationship between a machine that can produce writing and a human writer.In cyber-social relation, here are some tedious things the Generative AI machine will be able to do much better than a human teacher.",
    "We've already mentioned teaching phonics.",
    "It will be able to offer on-the-fly feedback as students learn to write.",
    "In the academic and disciplinary literacies of secondary and college education, Generative AI is particularly adept at \"genre signals\" (Hart-Davidson 2024).",
    "Keystroke capture will be able to work out the extent of the help provided by the machine."
  ]
}